{"tid":1985306,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良：待28日內無新增本地感染個案　才能完全解除限制","createTime":"2020-04-23T05:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T10:14:44.000Z","uid":166360,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e945c38755fffb24a1a0908ccd87d717c45fc6c","tid":1985306,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"香港新冠肺炎新增確診個案近日維持在單位數，零星本地感染個案亦能夠追蹤源頭。香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良今(23日)在電台節目表示，本地傳播情況正在紓緩，在中斷社區傳播方面見到曙光。他指若能維持現時的形勢，預料在下月7日，即最新一宗本地個案的兩星期後，可考慮放寬部分防疫措施，但仍要待28日內都無新增本地感染個案，才能完全解除限制措施。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良表示，香港最後一宗未能找到源頭的本地感染個案是本月19日的地勤人員個案。而最嚴重的酒吧群組，最後一宗個案就已於本月10日接受隔離，其他都是找到源頭的個案。<br />\n<br />\n他以2003年沙士作例子，指世衞當年於4月2日向香港發旅遊警示，5月23日解除，一個月後宣布香港無本地傳播個案，當中參考的數據，包括確診數字是否有明顯下降趨勢，是否沒有向外傳播個案，以及本地個案是否屬零星單位數等，上述幾個條件香港都大致能做到。如果香港能繼續做好防疫措施，傳播鏈中斷的日子就現曙光。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200423/bkn-20200423100143497-0423_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200423%2Fbkn-20200423100143497-0423_00822_001.html&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6u8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=bd8eefe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200423/bkn-20200423100143497-0423_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;他指若能維持現時的形勢，預料在下月7日，即最新一宗本地個案的兩星期後，可考慮放寬部分防疫措施&quot;<br />\n何生，你問過恐懼撚未呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f7b68d4cd23e69b685502c71cdcc6d8d72e5f6","tid":1985306,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:14:43.000Z","msg":"28日後 X N"},{"pid":"a8d890f927d9f9fcb9dad7b54f48494788d04634","tid":1985306,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"輸入計唔計"},{"pid":"941a42d41970a16c6f26c85c2dad2b620dc651fd","tid":1985306,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d890f927d9f9fcb9dad7b54f48494788d04634","tid":1985306,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"輸入計唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"&quot;要待28日內都無新增本地感染個案，才能完全解除限制措施&quot;<br />\n<br />\n唔計<br />\n<br />\n不過就算要28日無新增本地感染個案都是太過嚴苛"},{"pid":"2851a2e8bfc23ffec9d2f51b3cd48dd2a74b8e98","tid":1985306,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6u8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=346f6994\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a82252b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n&quot;現時本港大約有5%的患者需入住深切治療部，但當年沙士有四分一患者需深切治療部&quot;<br />\n&quot;現時很多仍然留院的病人都很精神，毋須利用儀器供氧，甚至可以在病房玩電話或做運動，只是等待病毒檢測呈陰性反應&quot;<br />\n&quot;病人失去味覺和嗅覺的情況都很短暫，亦只有少部分病人有肺部纖維化情況&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>都話左疫情被誇大啦</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84e5dfc4444715896b2c490bf5b3595a71ddba2","tid":1985306,"uid":54627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1A2iB09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1A2iB09.png&h=83960e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7df38e25d0d1bdf83e9142f9b50cd7dbef42f486","tid":1985306,"uid":62321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a84e5dfc4444715896b2c490bf5b3595a71ddba2","tid":1985306,"uid":54627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1A2iB09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna